item.title: Cameron County update for June 27 - July 4: 694 confirmed cases, 61% were contracted through community, 35% were linked...
item.description: Cameron County update for June 27 - July 4: 694 confirmed cases, 61% were contracted through community, 35% were linked to a previous case, and 4% were from travel. 35% were in the age range of 20 - 29, 20 in the age range 30 - 39, and 15 in the age range 40 - 49. 59% of the cases have been from Brownsville. Stay safe RGV!

item.description: Hidalgo County update for July 26 - June 3: 2,085 confirmed cases, 24% were in the age range of 20 - 29, 17% were in the age range of 30 - 39, 17% were in the age range of 40 - 49, and 17% were from Mission. 16% were from McAllen and 15% were from Edinburg. Analyzing the cases over the last week help show who is getting infect and from where. Stay safe RGV!

item.description: There's so many ways technology could improve the Valley. Rgvcovid19cases.com is just one - we're working on other projects we can't wait to share. We'll be posting deeper analytics on all of the officially reported coronavirus cases in the RGV on our Facebook page and you can see them on the website too. Like us on Facebook to support!
